|   MinIO     |       |   FastAPI  |       |  Redis  |       |  Celery     |
| (Video      +------>+ (Webhook   +------>+ (Broker +------>+ Workers     |
| Storage)    |       |  Handler)  |       |         |       | (GPU)       |
+-------------+       +------------+       +---------+       +------+------+
